title: Double BBQ-Spiced Chicken Drumsticks with Roast Potatoes, Pear Slaw & Salsa Verde
description: These spiced chicken drumsticks bring a smokey flavour punch you didn’t see coming! Paired with crispy roast potatoes, a refreshing pear slaw and a zesty salsa verde, this dish is a perfect balance of juicy, crunchy and herby goodness. Get ready for a seriously tasty twist on your classic chicken dinner!
